    <title>Asus’s new Zenbook 14X is the latest thin and light laptop with an OLED screen</title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="The Asus Zenbook 14X facing away from the camera, angled to the right, half open, on a white background." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/MBZ2T4WQRXJkPYGrvIy9a290FiE=/0x334:2000x1667/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/69808604/Zenbook_14X_OLED_UX5400_Product_photo_Pine_Grey_Thin_and_light.0.png" /&gt;
