  &lt;p id="02u16J"&gt;Locast has announced that it is suspending its TV streaming service starting today, following a &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2021/9/1/22652988/broadcaster-victory-locast-abc-nbc-fox-cbs"&gt;court ruling earlier this week&lt;/a&gt; in a lawsuit from ABC, CBS, Fox, and NBC, which &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2019/7/31/20748677/locast-streaming-tv-lawsuit-abc-cbs-fox-nbc"&gt;jointly sued the nonprofit service&lt;/a&gt; shortly after it launched. &lt;/p&gt;
